                    <p>This is a brief exploration into the link between thermodynamics, the limits of computation and logical irreversibility.</p>                   
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="container-post">
                <a href="@Url.Action("LorenzAttractor", "Posts")">
                    
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="/Images/LorenzAttractor_sm-trans.png" />
